  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: eea01f052d33de843ba353d44b00a9ac, type: 3}
  m_Name: BarnabasNode2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  options:
  - optionText: "I\u2019ve brought the packages you asked for."
    replyText: Thank you, traveler! This means a lot to our village. Alright, now
      we can talk about the Farm Restorer.
    nextNode: 2
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 4
    questID: 1
    objectID: 206
    amountObject: 3
    actions:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 98536571420870c4c933d2a7091d20b3, type: 2}
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1e137e6bdd421b341a5976662fca4198, type: 2}
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9d3d521b48aee5f41a7e0fc693785923, type: 2}
  - optionText: Where exactly is the station?
    replyText: The station is to the east of the village. Follow the main road until
      you see a small building with fuel pumps. Be careful, there are dangers lurking
      in that area.
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 7
    questID: 0
    objectID: 206
    amountObject: 3
    actions: []
  - optionText: What should I expect at the station?
    replyText: "Rumors speak of bandits and mutated creatures roaming around the
      station. Some of them have made it their home. You\u2019ll need to be ready
      for a fight if you want to retrieve the supply packages."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 7
    questID: 0
    objectID: 206
    amountObject: 3
    actions: []
  - optionText: "Alright, I\u2019ll take care of it."
    replyText: Thank you, traveler. Our village really needs those supplies. Come
      back to me when you have them. Good luck!
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 1
    questID: 1
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 076003089f26b4f478ee1cbafcf8e4ea, type: 2}
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 2022859919feff24ba7d136254e4cd0e, type: 2}
  - optionText: What happened to your eye?
    replyText: "That\u2019s a long story\u2026 Before Clearwater even existed, I
      was traveling with a caravan. One night, bandits from Texas attacked us - I
      was the only one who made it out alive. I killed them all with my shotgun\u2026
      but one of their bullets damaged my eye."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
  - optionText: "Do you have a wife\u2026 or is it just you and your son, Colby?"
    replyText: "I don\u2019t have a wife. Not anymore. She died giving birth\u2026
      Back then, there wasn\u2019t even a doctor in the village. It\u2019s just been
      me and the boy since. I\u2019m doing what I can to raise him right."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
  - optionText: Thank you, I have to go now.
    replyText: 
    nextNode: 0
    exitOption: 1
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
